						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying near a ruined temple to the west of the village.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of land for providing offerings to the temple Raḍḍigaḍla at Śāsanapumbrōlu made in the time of Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Kūmāra Biruduṁ-Gāmarāju.</p>						

